| **Thriving** | Integration & Efficiency | Optimize systems, connect data across functions, and develop leadership layers for scalable execution. | From *Builder* to *Architect* — moving from hands-on management to strategic oversight using data and culture. | A scalable organization operating through leadership depth and integrated intelligence. |
